12.short_description: Passto is a live entertainment marketing and e-ticketing company.

18.description:
Our project started with an idea in 2012. The goal was to get rid of paper tickets for events, saving purchasing time, expediting entry and reducing the amount of paper issued.
 

We created a software for producers to sell online and box office, using the latest technology available in the market and allowing viewers to enter events with maximum security.

After processing the sale of tickets and access to more than 250,000 people, our software was sold in April 2016 to DF Entertainment / C3 Presents (Live Nation Group), the producer of Lollapalooza Festival.

Currently our technology is still used for the sale and access of the biggest shows in Latin America under another brand and another company.

18.description:
Restorius is an App. and a website with user-generated content, specialized in recipes, video cookbook, online grocery shopping focused on Spanish speaking users. 
It’s a place where Spanish speaking users can explore and learn about the classic & contemporary Latin recipes.
They focus on website on recipes and create a site with user-generated content to be the US spanish & Latin American market leader, capitalizing on online advertising, discovery shopping opportunity, brand publishing and food e-commerce.
Restorius simultaneously entertains and educates its aficionados about Latin ingredients and transports them to the epicenters of Latin food culture at their source. As a brand and an entertainment and news source, Restorius features chef personalities from South America who create and enjoy Latin food, along with video cookbook and online cooking classes, all in Spanish from Latin America.
